enhanced_by.reason: The addTags method must be invoked before removeTags to ensure that the tags being removed were previously allowed.
Environment setup is required before modifying the safelist to ensure consistent state.
The isSafeTag method can be used to verify that the tags removed by removeTags are no longer considered safe.
Both methods involve modifying the safelist by removing tags, making verifyTagRemoval a suitable method for asserting the effects of removeTags.
